com.concordium.sdk.transactions

Class AccountTransactionV1

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.concordium.sdk.transactions.BlockItem
      • com.concordium.sdk.transactions.AccountTransactionV1
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Transaction

    public class AccountTransactionV1
extends BlockItem
    An extended transaction format originating from a particular account. Such a transaction can be sponsored, in which case its cost is not paid by the sender.
    See Also:
    Transaction factory, that lets create and complete sponsored transactions
